            <title><![CDATA[March 2026]]></title>
            <link>https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-03-changelog</link>
            <guid>https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-03-changelog</guid>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 08:10:02 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[Provides an overview of key updates to Suprema Docs from February through March.]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>This March update improves your <strong>Suprema Docs</strong> experience with a more intuitive interface and enhanced search functionality. Meanwhile, the BioStar Air Administrator Guide has been completely restructured to help you understand all features—from user management to access control and video surveillance—at a glance.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" alt="Suprema Docs 26.03 Changelogs" src="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/assets/images/changelogs-202603-c15b7331f076c3d94af5e3a46090a663.png" width="800" height="394" class="img_ev3q"></p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="docs">Docs<a href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-03-changelog#docs" class="hash-link" aria-label="Enlace directo a Docs" title="Enlace directo a Docs" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p>Redesigned home page</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" alt="Suprema Docs home" src="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/assets/images/changelog-03-home-ea316261191418e4109ce742dbb21e43.png" width="1437" height="1148" class="img_ev3q"></p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Enhanced search functionality</p>
<p>Added product-specific search and keyboard shortcut (Ctrl + K) to open the search bar</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" alt="Suprema Docs home" src="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/assets/images/changelog-03-search-2bc412d1eb46e0cfe28cf766e016cd2c.png" width="1920" height="1080" class="img_ev3q"></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="platform">Platform<a href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-03-changelog#platform" class="hash-link" aria-label="Enlace directo a Platform" title="Enlace directo a Platform" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="biostar-x">BioStar X<a href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-03-changelog#biostar-x" class="hash-link" aria-label="Enlace directo a BioStar X" title="Enlace directo a BioStar X" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class="">Updated documentation for <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/platform/biostar_x/settings-video-integration">VMS Server Integration and Certificate Installation</a></li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="biostar-air">BioStar Air<a href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-03-changelog#biostar-air" class="hash-link" aria-label="Enlace directo a BioStar Air" title="Enlace directo a BioStar Air" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p>Completed comprehensive restructuring and optimization of the <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/platform/biostar_air">BioStar Air Administrator Guide</a></p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Expanded multilingual support for BioStar Air: English, Japanese, and Spanish translations added</p>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p>Added documentation for key features including user management, access rights management, and video management</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Added English interface images and user interface screenshots</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Improved BioStar Air table of contents structure and reorganized sections</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="devices">Devices<a href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-03-changelog#devices" class="hash-link" aria-label="Enlace directo a Devices" title="Enlace directo a Devices" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Added new release notes and updated existing device documentation.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="device-documentation-updates">Device Documentation Updates<a href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-03-changelog#device-documentation-updates" class="hash-link" aria-label="Enlace directo a Device Documentation Updates" title="Enlace directo a Device Documentation Updates" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class=""><a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/device/xpass_2/release-notes/151">XPass 2</a>: Added v1.5.1 release notes</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p><a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/device/device_manager/release-notes/122">Device Manager</a>: Established new app release notes category and added v1.2.2 release notes</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p><a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/device/bioentry_p2/release-notes/160">BioEntry P2</a>: Added v1.6.0 release notes</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Added instructional images for device factory reset button location</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="developer">Developer<a href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-03-changelog#developer" class="hash-link" aria-label="Enlace directo a Developer" title="Enlace directo a Developer" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p>API documentation updated: <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/api/bsxapi#tag/Cards/operation/createCard">Create BioStar X QR</a></p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Device SDK: Added v2.9.12 release notes</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="multilingual-support">Multilingual Support<a href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-03-changelog#multilingual-support" class="hash-link" aria-label="Enlace directo a Multilingual Support" title="Enlace directo a Multilingual Support" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p>Improved documentation quality for Japanese and Spanish versions</p>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p>Enhanced consistency of document titles and content</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Corrected mistranslations and standardized terminology</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Fixed spacing and grammar issues</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Significantly updated English translation</p>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p>Standardized technical terminology</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Improved sentence structure and phrasing</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="open-source-software-licenses">Open Source Software Licenses<a href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-03-changelog#open-source-software-licenses" class="hash-link" aria-label="Enlace directo a Open Source Software Licenses" title="Enlace directo a Open Source Software Licenses" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">Added license attributions: <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/legal/open-source-licenses#the-2-clause-bsd-license">BSD-2-Clause</a>, <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/legal/open-source-licenses#the-3-clause-bsd-license">BSD-3-Clause</a>, <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/legal/open-source-licenses#eclipse-public-license">EPL</a>, <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/legal/open-source-licenses#eclipse-distribution-license">EDL</a>, <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/legal/open-source-licenses#gnu-lesser-general-public-v21-license">LGPLv2.1</a>​, <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/legal/open-source-licenses#gnu-general-public-v2-license">GPLv2</a>​, <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/legal/open-source-licenses#isc-license">ISC</a>, <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/legal/open-source-licenses#zlib-license">zlib</a></li>
</ul>]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[January 2026]]></title>
            <link>https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-01-02-changelog</link>
            <guid>https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-01-02-changelog</guid>
            <pubDate>Fri, 02 Jan 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[Provides an overview of updates since the initial launch of Suprema Docs through December.]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>Suprema Docs</strong> is a knowledge hub that brings together all product manuals and technical documentation in one place. It includes the following key documentation:</p>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p><strong>Product manuals</strong>: Installation and user manuals for Suprema products</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p><strong>Solution manuals</strong></p>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p>User manual for BioStar X</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>User manual for BioStar Air (coming soon)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="">
<p><strong>Technical documents</strong>: APIs and other technical resources</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p><strong>Release Notes</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>Below is a summary of the key updates for January 2026.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" alt="Suprema Docs" src="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/assets/images/changelogs-202501-5714a8beee7b8e2a3ee6b62a3e11c908.png" width="800" height="394" class="img_ev3q"></p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="biostar-x">BioStar X<a href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-01-02-changelog#biostar-x" class="hash-link" aria-label="Enlace directo a BioStar X" title="Enlace directo a BioStar X" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p>Added <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/platform/biostar_x/release-notes/101">BioStar X v1.0.1 Release Notes</a></p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Added guide for <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/platform/biostar_x/enroll-credential-ir-face">IR Face</a> credentials</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Added guide for <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/platform/biostar_x/settings-remote-access">Remote Access</a> configuration and usage</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Added guide for integrating event logs using the <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/platform/biostar_x/settings-virtual-device-event-log">Virtual Device</a> feature</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Updated guides for the ability to enter a reason when exporting or printing user, data, and audit trail menus</p>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p><a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/platform/biostar_x/export-import-user-info">Export/Import User Information</a></p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p><a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/platform/biostar_x/data-generate-reports">Generate Report</a></p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p><a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/platform/biostar_x/settings-system-audit-trail">Manage Audit Trail</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Updated <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/platform/biostar_x/licensing">License Policy</a> details</p>
<ul>
<li class="">
<p>Added description that devices cannot be added without a Base License</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Added description of limit on the number of Ethernet-connected devices</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Added description of maximum administrator count</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Added <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/api/bsxapi">BioStar X API</a> documentation</p>
</li>
<li class="">
<p>Added <a class="" href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/bsx-license-calculator">BioStar X License Calculator</a> page to help with complex licensing requirements</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="devices">Devices<a href="https://supremainc.github.io/docs/es/changelog/2026-01-02-changelog#devices" class="hash-link" aria-label="Enlace directo a Devices" title="Enlace directo a Devices" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Updated all the latest device manuals. The device manuals available in <strong>Suprema Docs</strong> are as follows:</p>
